title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Schiphol Airport (EHAM)
description:
In this video we will have a look at the free addon for Schiphol Airport (EHAM) which has been out for a few weeks but has received massive updates. If you are a fan of this airport this is almost a must have for you because it adds a lot of detail which is missing from the default MSFS content.

If you would like to try the scenery yourself, download it via the link below:
https://flightsim.to/file/31203/eham-amsterdam-airport-scenery-enhancements-premium-deluxe

In addition to the download above it is strongly recommended to also add the following 3 addons:

Dave's 3D People library
https://flightsim.to/file/5452/dave-s-3d-people-library

Dutch Emergency Vehicle Package
https://flightsim.to/file/28484/dutch-emergency-vehicle-pack

jhd library:
https://flightsim.to/file/28208/jhd-library
